---
---

<section id="pricing" style="padding:96px 5%;text-align:center">
  <div class="reveal">
    <span class="sec-label">Tarifs</span>
    <h2>Simple et <em>transparent</em></h2>
    <p style="color:var(--txt2);font-size:17px;font-weight:300;max-width:460px;margin:0 auto">Journal trading gratuit pour démarrer, sans CB. Passe Premium quand tu es prêt — essai 7 jours inclus. Prix en euros TTC, facturé depuis la France 🇫🇷.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="price-grid reveal" style="transition-delay:.1s">
    <div class="price-card">
      <div class="price-name">Gratuit</div>
      <div class="price-amt">
        <span class="price-amt-num">0</span>
        <span class="price-amt-cur">€</span>
      </div>
      <div class="price-period">pour toujours · sans CB requise</div>
      <div class="price-divider"></div>
      <ul class="price-feats" style="margin-top:24px">
        <li>50 trades par mois</li>
        <li>Journal complet — émotions, setup, notes</li>
        <li>Tracking émotionnel</li>
        <li>Stats de base — win rate, P&amp;L, top session, heure top</li>
        <li>Historique illimité</li>
        <li class="no">Analytics avancés — heatmap, courbes, top actifs</li>
        <li class="no">IA Insights &amp; Chat coach</li>
        <li class="no">Weekly Debrief automatique</li>
        <li class="no">Score trader</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="https://app.mytradingcoach.app/register" class="price-cta ghost">Commencer gratuitement</a>
    </div>
    <div class="price-card feat" style="padding-top:44px">
      <div class="price-pop">⭐ Recommandé</div>
      <div class="price-name">Premium</div>
      <div class="price-amt">
        <span class="price-amt-num">39</span>
        <span class="price-amt-cur">€</span>
        <span class="price-amt-per">/mois</span>
      </div>
      <div class="price-period">ou 349 €/an — tu économises 119 €</div>
      <div class="price-divider"></div>
      <ul class="price-feats" style="margin-top:24px">
        <li>Trades illimités</li>
        <li>Tout le plan FREE inclus</li>
        <li>Analytics avancés — heatmap, equity curve, top actifs, setup</li>
        <li>✨ IA Insights — analyse de tes patterns par Claude <small class="feat-limit">(1 analyse toutes les 4h)</small></li>
        <li>💬 Chat coach IA personnalisé <small class="feat-limit">(50 messages/jour)</small></li>
        <li>📅 Weekly Debrief automatique chaque dimanche</li>
        <li>Score trader — 5 axes de progression</li>
        <li>Export PDF des debriefs</li>
        <li>Hébergé en France 🇫🇷 · Données chiffrées</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="https://app.mytradingcoach.app/register?plan=premium" class="price-cta prim">Essayer 7 jours gratuit →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .price-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 56px auto 0;
  }

  .price-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--b);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 36px 32px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .price-card.feat {
    border-color: rgba(59,130,246,.4);
    background: linear-gradient(160deg,rgba(59,130,246,.07),rgba(139,92,246,.04));
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(59,130,246,.08);
    position: relative;
  }

  .price-pop {
    position: absolute;
    top: -14px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    padding: 4px 14px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    background: var(--card);
    color: var(--blue2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,.4);
    letter-spacing: .3px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .price-divider { height: 1px; background: var(--b); margin: 22px 0; }

  .price-name {
    font-family: var(--disp);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--txt3);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .price-amt {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 3px;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .price-amt-num { font-family: var(--body); font-size: 36px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -.3px; line-height: 1; color: var(--txt); }
  .price-amt-cur { font-family: var(--body); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--txt2); line-height: 1; }
  .price-amt-per { font-family: var(--body); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--txt3); line-height: 1; }

  .price-period {
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: var(--txt3);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    letter-spacing: .2px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .price-feats {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .price-feats li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 11px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--txt2);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .price-feats li::before { content: '✓'; color: var(--green); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
  .price-feats li.no { color: var(--txt3); }
  .price-feats li.no::before { content: '–'; color: var(--txt3); font-weight: 400; }
  .feat-limit { font-size: 11px; color: var(--txt3); font-family: var(--mono); margin-left: 2px; }

  .price-cta {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 14px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all .2s;
    font-family: var(--disp);
    letter-spacing: -.1px;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .price-cta.prim { background: var(--blue); color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(59,130,246,.35); }
  .price-cta.prim:hover { background: var(--blue2); box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(59,130,246,.55); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .price-cta.ghost { border: 1px solid var(--b2); color: var(--txt2); }
  .price-cta.ghost:hover { border-color: var(--blue); color: var(--txt); background: rgba(59,130,246,.05); }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .price-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
